{"tid":843100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逼5歲女童喝尿、性侵還剃頭　小心！變態老闆只5萬港幣保釋 圖","createTime":"2018-10-01T01:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T01:36:20.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3167591726b884419e2f97aa99bf57ab0cf1bb","tid":843100,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"根據《自由時報》報導，王男自去年11月遭羈押以後，羈押期到今年10月1日屆滿，日前向桃園地院聲請具保停押，9月26日開庭後獲合議庭諭知以20萬元交保，限制出境、出海，每周一、三、五須到居住處的新北市板橋警分局板橋派出所報到。<br />\n當初偵辦此案的刑警對此氣憤說「這個人做出罪無可逭的暴行，怎麼能把他放了！萬一又犯案，法官要負責嗎？」，法界人士也憂心，王男被放出來「恐有再犯之虞」，直言「讓他交保在外，將造成人心惶惶！」<br />\n檢警當時調查，王男(28歲)念大學時，曾參加校方輔導成立食物銀行公司解決食物浪費，還獲得教育部「大專畢業生創業服務計畫(U-Start計畫)」入選績優創業團隊，在校就與朋友合夥在龍潭經營即期商品店；當時他承諾林姓單親媽媽會幫忙照顧5歲女童，對她說「我在多所小學當過補救教學老師，不用擔心。」林女也才放心將女兒交給對方，卻想不到對方做出這些非人所為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181001/1439271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181001%2F1439271&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ad87f09e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181001%2F1439271&h=0d43e964\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181001/1439271</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181001/640_4f9dadc0724fdf81146b91aa0fb2474e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181001%2F640_4f9dadc0724fdf81146b91aa0fb2474e.jpg&h=e2e93488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181001/640_ff18c5ff49e364f05ca3c59412ca1ab0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181001%2F640_ff18c5ff49e364f05ca3c59412ca1ab0.jpg&h=b707e61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7281071cd7821df4b64398c6a0609